 Research Influence


 CLOCK-Pro (USENIX'05) has been adopted in OS and data management systems (See 
source code in NetBSD, 
a LinuxMM article, 
and more details). 
  



Hystor (ICS'11) has influenced commercial hybrid storage products, including Apple's Fusion Drive (See a CCC report, and more details). 
  


